    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2013 BMW M3 is a stunning example of the legendary S65 V8 era, finished in a timeless Mineral White Metallic over a well-preserved black Novillo leather interior. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, boasting a comprehensive service history that includes the critical rod bearing replacement and regular throttle actuator maintenance. The exterior remains sharp and glossy, though a close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel, consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the leather is supple, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All features, from the responsive iDrive system to the dual-zone climate control, operate exactly as intended. It sits on factory Competition Package wheels wrapped in Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires with plenty of tread remaining. This is a reliable, turn-key enthusiast vehicle that perfectly balances raw high-revving performance with daily drivability.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
